                        "id": "18107769241386237",
                        "text": "\ud83d\udccdKoffee Mameya Kakeru, Tokyo | #koffeemameyakakeru\n\nWe left @koffee_mameya_kakeru feeling like we just watched a spectacular concert \ud83e\udd29\n\nKoffee Mameya Kakeru leans completely into its philosophy of \u2018kakeru\u2019 which means \u2018to multiply\u2019 or the concept of various elements coming together to create something more significant and valuable than each individual part.\n\nFocusing on the Japanese concept of \u2018kodawari\u2019 - aspiration to perfection and attention to detail, the master brewers at Koffee Mameya Kakeru focus on stretching coffee\u2019s potential and delivering the best cup possible. \n\nTasting courses start at \u00a53500, which comes with 3 drinks brewed using different methods, accompanied by complementing sweets. Premium coffee course and cocktail coffee course are available too! \n\nNote: The banana au-lait in the video was an a-la-carte order\n\nReservations are a MUST and is available on their page\n\nFor more perks and curated gems, \n\u2605 linktr.ee/shoyutheworld\n\n#japancafe #japancoffee #tokyocoffee #tokyocafe #tokyo"
                    }
                }
            ]
        },
